04/07/2003
ROME, Italy -- Army Chief of Staff Gen Mosca Moschini met with his Albanian counterpart, Maj Gen Pellumb Qazimi, on Thursday (3 July). Both agreed that their countries had reached a good level of military co-operation. Qazimi briefed Moschini on progress made in restructuring the armed forces. The talks were particularly significant now that Italy has assumed the rotating EU presidency. (ATA, BBC - 03/07/03)
